com.koloboke.collect

Interface LongIterator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterator<Long>, PrimitiveIterator<Long,LongConsumer>, PrimitiveIterator.OfLong

    public interface LongIterator
extends Iterator<Long>, PrimitiveIterator.OfLong
    Primitive specialization of Iterator<Long>.

    See the comparison of iteration ways in the library.

    Iterators of updatable and immutable collections don't support Iterator.remove() operation. More about mutability profiles.

    See Also:
    LongCollection.iterator()
